    "30812": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "I guess I could give this a go."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "30811": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Hey cutie."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "You're going to help me out too? How kind of you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Don't hesitate to come to me if you need anything."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What kind of things does a librarian do?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Good question."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Basically, things other than that which require brawn... or brains."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So... what does that leave?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Why would a librarian be at the ruins...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Hmm... Good question."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Well, because Jean trusts me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "So you should as well."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "30803": {
        "Desc": "Explore the temple's depths",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "I'm Lisa, the librarian. Do you need anything, cutie?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'd like to know more about monsters."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "The monsters out in the wild? We've got many resources here in the library."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Making good use of elemental advantages is the key to winning any battle."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "By the way, would you be interested in having a part-time job here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "We need people to... need people for doing... We just need more people."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "How do we fight Stormterror?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "A way to fight against Stormterror..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "I'm sorry, but there's no way to do it alone."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Judging by the level of its Anemo power, it's definitely not an ordinary creature."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "I could teach you some elemental basics, so you'll have an idea of what I'm talking about."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Goodbye."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Heading out? See you in a bit."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "30814": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Lisa",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Dragon of the East, Lion of the South, Wolf of the North, Falcon of the West..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "They are the Four Winds of Mondstadt, affiliated with Barbatos, the God of Anemo."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "The Dragon of the East, Stormterror — its real name, is Dvalin."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Though most in Mondstadt seem to have forgotten that in all this \"Stormterror\" business."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "So now you know why Dvalin is only able to channel three of the Four Winds' power."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Because it has been consuming itself from the beginning."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Why?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Why would it go to such lengths?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Because of hatred, I presume."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hatred...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Hatred for Mondstadt."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Hatred drove it to become something more powerful than the wind itself — to become Stormterror."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But why would one of The Four Winds..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hate the city it was supposed to protect?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "As a child of Mondstadt, it's something that's really hard to say aloud."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lisa",
                    "T": "Here, take this. It's a very old story from more than a century ago."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
