    "30712": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Let me show you how the Knights of Favonius conquer our adversaries!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "30711": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "You've arrived."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Come closer. Can you smell that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "...I can't smell anything."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's the smell of burnt Pyro Slimes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Something must have happened in the <color=#00E1FFFF>temple</color>."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "I imagine there will be slimes, hilichurls, and... whatever is giving Stormterror extra power."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Oh yes, it is going to be lively in there indeed!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Will it be dangerous?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "As bustling as it may be — no, I can't imagine it will be dangerous at all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "No doubt nothing more than a disorderly mob of creatures."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Oh, ho-ho! You're quite the brave one, aren't you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "It's a pity that the Temple of the Wolf has been disturbed by such an atrocity."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "#Let's head in, {NICKNAME}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "No one makes offerings to The Four Winds anymore, yet the old winds never vanish..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "We need to clear out the temples, for The Four Winds."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "30703": {
        "Desc": "Explore the temple's depths",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "You're not bad with that wind glider. Your gliding style seems familiar..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "How'd you get your eye patch?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "My eye patch? Wanna hear my story, eh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "I didn't have time to introduce myself properly... Well, it wasn't on my mind to begin with."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Ehe... My apologies. I'm Kaeya, Cavalry Captain for the Knights of Favonius."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "We can talk more after we get things sorted."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "I know a great place more fit for a chat."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Why is Jean the Acting Grand Master?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "The Grand Master is currently off leading an expedition, so the Master, Jean, has stepped in to oversee the Knights while he's gone."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Hence, you'll hear many refer to her as the Acting Grand Master."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "When the Grand Master left, he took the vast majority of our knights with him, leaving the Acting Grand Master with far more responsibility and stress."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Come to think of it, it must have been difficult for Jean."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Goodbye."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "See you later then."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "30715": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Kaeya",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Bravo! What a performance!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "You are, to my surprise, a well-trained knight."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "The battles you just fought were sights to behold."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Thanks, that's nice of you to say..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Not worth complimenting really..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Haha, I see you already have the knightly virtue of modesty."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Stories of your heroic deeds to save Mondstadt from destruction shall be known throughout the City of Freedom, well into the future."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Please do visit me at our headquarters when you have the time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "I also know a lovely tavern, if that's more your thing."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
