    "30612": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Everyone in Mondstadt is still getting blown about by the storm..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Every second we waste is a mark against the name of Favonius. Let's get in that temple, stat!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "30611": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "This is it. One of the deserted <color=#00E1FFFF>temples of The Four Winds</color>."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "These temples have been left to waste for years now. The people of Mondstadt almost never come here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "There's a chance there's a monster nest or a hilichurl camp inside."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Even Stormterror has given up on its own temple."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "\"Stormterror...\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Wait, did you just say \"its own temple...\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "...Yes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "I also find it hard to accept, but... Stormterror was once one of The Four Winds."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ehhhh!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Wait... Did you just feel that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "The wind here... Something's off..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "#Let's go in and take a look, {NICKNAME}. Be careful, the dragon's power is disturbing this area."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "30603": {
        "Desc": "Explore the temple's depths",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Wanna team up with me? Huh, I should warn you though, I don't slow down for anyone, greenhorn or otherwise."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Jean seems to be pretty reliable."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "With Jean by our side, nothing can stand in our way! ...At least, that's what I wanna say..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "But I can't keep spouting that same old line."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "She always dashes headlong into the heat of the battle, and we want her to take better care of herself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "I really hope that one day I can look Jean in the eye and tell her she doesn't need to worry anymore, because we have her back..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You seem pretty good with a wind glider."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "As a novice within the Knights of Favonius, your understanding of the wind is absolutely crucial."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Leave the advanced wind glider training to me!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Goodbye."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Let's all do our best to defeat Stormterror!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "30610": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Amber",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Phew, I'm tired."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "But, at least this way we've helped Jean out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "In the past, we were at least able to defend the city and keep it safe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "This, of course, is mostly thanks to Jean."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "But now with Stormterror directly attacking the city itself..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "\"The winds change, so too should our tactics.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sounds deep."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Did you come up with it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "It's what Lisa likes to say."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Speaking of which, The Four Winds we were discussing earlier..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "If you want to learn more about our history, you can ask Lisa."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "...I'm not saying I don't know our history! It's just..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "I mean... A librarian is supposed to be more knowledgeable than an Outrider, right?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
